brazilian red meat output down sharpli - usda brazilian red meat product in 1986 fell more than 20 pct to 1.9 mln tonn due to drought which reduc slaughter weight and to herd rebuild which start becau of high cattl price , the u.s. agricultur depart said . in it report on world product and trade develop , usda said that in 1987 , beef product is expect to reach 2.3 mln tonn . pork product in 1986 rose 83 pct to 1.1 mln tonn due to the sharp rise in beef price and is expect to remain at that level thi year , usda said .